title: Guacamole
reviews: Friendly staff, 30 or so places to sit, and all the staples on the menu (carnitas, chicken, Barbacoa, carne asada, etc.).-- Amanda
One of my friends had a super burrito EXTRA spicy and the other had a wet super burrito-- Tom
Bean dip very good, hot and a generous amount for the price!-- David
